{"tid":862013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明日大嶼人工島計劃似唔似東方華爾街個個明日基金？","createTime":"2018-10-14T14:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T14:42:41.000Z","uid":72280,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea7b20cf11706489ba60c5d405211560a5f8418d","tid":862013,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/221308_cf89fe543f6945d4fb708107646687aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F221308_cf89fe543f6945d4fb708107646687aa.png&h=9750a685&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/221321_bb93708251a191f27c99e5cc1062c523.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F221321_bb93708251a191f27c99e5cc1062c523.png&h=0381cd46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/221324_cf89fe543f6945d4fb708107646687aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F221324_cf89fe543f6945d4fb708107646687aa.png&h=35967b12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3da944485250ebc0b96dc3fd29ac937a2d5ea1b5","tid":862013,"uid":72280,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:22:12.000Z","msg":"　　葉抱一當上金管部的總裁並不是幸運，而是他提出了一個叫做「明日基金」的項目。這個項目向廣大市民銷售，並且基金款項轉化為基建撥款用來盈利，這樣既緩解了政府的壓力，又對民眾有利有益。當日，立法院已經通過對「明日基金」的初審，可就在第二天三讀的時候，韋航突然出現在立法院，用煙頭引發火災，並且甩下一大摞資料，說「明日基金」是個騙局，因此「明日基金」項目的裁決就此停止，打算下星期繼續審理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明日基金看起來像是服務了廣大市民，還發展了基建，但其實是各大財團和葉抱一的陰謀，如果明日基金項目通過，那麼以後各大財團圈錢就再也不用通過立法院<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/222209_d69b832204b9020dd247d4d751da5252.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F222209_d69b832204b9020dd247d4d751da5252.png&h=762c75d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71a0d9f3a3925c